file_content.text: Jedi! Alert base and assume battle positions!
Republic forces! Alert base and assume battle positions!
Intruders! Alert base and assume battle positions!
Retarget the torture droids. Release the Killiks if you have to! We can take the enemy's very best.
You've done enough already. I won't let you hurt anyone else.
I'm going to stop you.
I know you turned the Killiks against House Organa.
I'm going to stop you.
You don't know anything about this, Jedi. And you're never going to learn.
You may talk big, but you've never fought Havoc Squad.
We'll see about that!
You want to brag, or you want to shoot? I can do both.
Bring on the fight.
You've got a smart mouth. Maybe I'll turn the droids on you when they need a break from the Killiks.
Surrender your weapons, and you and your men can leave in peace.
Get out of here.
I've won a dozen battles for the king himself. I can win against Republic dogs.
You're pathetic.
For House Ulgo! For the crown!
Hold your ground. You aren't supposed to be here!
Is that so? Huh. All right. I know a losing battle when I see it.
Move out, men. You can have the cave and the Killiks--but watch out. They bite.
